Package jetbrains.mps.openapi.editor.cells

Interface CellInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultCellInfo
    public interface CellInfo
    This interface can be used to remember the cell in order to find it later in (another instance of) the editor.

    User: shatalin Date: 01/06/16
